# CGraph — Incomplete Features & Implementation Priorities

> Comprehensive inventory of every stub, placeholder, missing integration, and half-finished feature across the codebase. Prioritized for completion, not deletion.
>
> **Last updated:** 2026-02-18 — 20 of 20 items resolved or implemented

---

## Priority Legend

| Priority | Meaning | Impact |
|----------|---------|--------|
| **P0** | Blocks deployment or core functionality | Must complete before launch |
| **P1** | Major feature gap visible to users | Required for v1.0 |
| **P2** | Noticeable but non-blocking | Target for v1.1 |
| **P3** | Nice-to-have, polish item | Post-launch |

---

## 🔴 P0 — Blocks Core Functionality

### 1. Stripe Payment Integration (Premium Subscriptions) ✅ IMPLEMENTED

**Status:** ~~Placeholder~~ → Real `Stripe.Checkout.Session.create` call wired up (2026-02-17)

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| [premium_controller.ex](file:///CGraph/apps/backend/lib/cgraph_web/controllers/premium_controller.ex#L214-L255) | `create_checkout_session` now calls `Stripe.Checkout.Session.create` with proper params, success/cancel URLs, and metadata. Returns `checkout_url` for frontend redirect. |
| [stripe_webhook_controller.ex](file:///CGraph/apps/backend/lib/cgraph_web/controllers/stripe_webhook_controller.ex) | Already fully implemented (handles subscription.created/updated/deleted, invoice events) |
| [BillingSettingsPanel.tsx](file:///CGraph/apps/web/src/modules/settings/components/panels/BillingSettingsPanel.tsx#L20-L23) | Already handles `checkout_url` redirect correctly |

**Remaining:** Set `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY`, `STRIPE_PREMIUM_PRICE_ID`, `STRIPE_PREMIUM_PLUS_PRICE_ID`, `STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET` env vars in production.

