## 🔵 P3 — Polish & Nice-to-Have

### 18. Telemetry Metrics Backend Placeholders ✅ IMPLEMENTED

**Status:** ~~Stub logging only~~ → Real Prometheus metrics export (2026-02-18)

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| telemetry.ex | `increment_counter` and `record_histogram` now emit real `:telemetry.execute` events AND record to `CGraph.Metrics` GenServer. Events flow through `TelemetryMetricsPrometheus.Core` for automatic Prometheus aggregation. |
| metrics_controller.ex | `/metrics` endpoint now combines output from both `CGraph.Metrics.export(:prometheus)` and `TelemetryMetricsPrometheus.Core.scrape(:cgraph_prometheus_metrics)`. Sets proper `text/plain; version=0.0.4` content type. |

### 19. Channel Drag-and-Drop Reordering ✅ IMPLEMENTED

**Status:** ~~@todo(ui) planned~~ → Full DnD with `@dnd-kit` + backend endpoint (2026-02-18)

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| channels.ex (backend) | New `reorder_channels(group, channel_ids)` — validates all IDs belong to group, batch-updates `position` field in a transaction |
| channel_controller.ex | New `reorder` action accepting `{"channel_ids": [...]}` |
| messaging_routes.ex | Added `PUT /groups/:group_id/channels/reorder` route |
| groups.ex | Added `defdelegate reorder_channels/2` |
| ChannelList.tsx | Wrapped with `DndContext` + `SortableContext` from `@dnd-kit/core` and `@dnd-kit/sortable` |
| SortableChannel.tsx | NEW: Sortable wrapper for `ChannelItem` with drag handles, transform, opacity |
| ChannelCategory.tsx | Uses `SortableChannel` instead of raw `ChannelItem` for DnD support |
| group-actions.ts | `updateChannelOrder` API endpoint updated to `PUT /channels/reorder` |
| package.json (web) | Added `@dnd-kit/core`, `@dnd-kit/sortable`, `@dnd-kit/utilities` |

